On Duke’s campaign website, the conservative slammed “our nation’s politicians” for compromising “too much,” leading to “radical policies that ruin America.”

The six SEALs, who include Morgan Luttrell of Texas’ 8th Congressional District, Brady Duke of Florida’s 7th District, Eli Crane of Arizona’s 2nd District, Derrick Van Orden of Wisconsin’s 3rd District, Ed Thelander of Maine’s 1st District, and Ryan Zinke of Montana’s 1st District, said in a new ad that Pelosi is the “one grave threat” they still face.
